sentences: Eddie Barbash is an American saxophonist known for his work as a core member of Jon Batiste and Stay Human, and was part of the house band for Late Show with Stephen Colbert through 2016.
In 2008 he began playing with Chico Hamilton and Jon Batiste.
In 2009, he formed The Amigos, an Americana band based in New York City.
He left The Amigos in 2013 to tour with Stay Human.
In 2015 Stay Human was announced as the house band for Late Show with Stephen Colbert.
Twelve Tones of Love (2009)With The Amigos
Diner In The Sky (2013)With Jon Batiste
The Late Show EP (2016)With Sam Evian
His family moved to Atlanta, Georgia when he was two years old.
Barbash was born in West Islip, New York, but spent his first years living in Oaxaca, Mexico.
At eight years old he began playing Saxophone in his elementary school band.
